record.description:
A bundle that contains MAVEN data return files from Electrical Power System; Guidance, Navigation and Control,
		NGMIS Instrument Data; Particle and Fields Instrument; Periapsis Timing Estimator; Remote Sensing (IUVS) Instrument; Solar Array Switching Modules;
		Universal Switching Modules and Inertial Measurement Unit. It also include mission events including events from the MAVEN Payload Operations Center events database, and MAVEN science events.
